rows.label: qst201508_msg0001
rows.name:
Mm? Friends asking Tolulu
about tenant's research?

rows.label: qst201508_msg0002
rows.name:
T-terrible sorries, but Tolulu only
deal with day-to-daycare of property.
Not know about business of tenant.

rows.label: qst201508_msg0003
rows.name:
Tolulu not know single thing,
so would appreciate if
friends could leave now!

rows.label: qst201508_msg0004
rows.name:
Mo-mo?! Tolulu feeling immense
weight of Noponic disapproval...

rows.label: qst201508_msg0008
rows.name:
Okay, Tolulu spill beans. But friends
promise not to tell! Promise?

rows.label: qst201508_msg0009
rows.name:
Tolulu employed by botanist
name of Lapacoll.

rows.label: qst201508_msg0010
rows.name:
He always shut away inside. Only
ever opens door for Tolulu.

rows.label: qst201508_msg0011
rows.name:
Needs special knock to get in. Need to
knock on door 16 times. It get sore on
Tolulu's wings. Friends maybe try that?

rows.label: qst201508_msg0012
rows.name:
Remember, not word came
from Tolulu's mouth!

rows.label: qst201508_msg0013
rows.name:
Tolulu hired to clean
property, not rat on tenants!

rows.label: qst201508_msg0014
rows.name:
Tolulu not tell anything, not
long as Tolulu paid to do job!
